                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-1604" type="given" value="CHARLES HENRY"></interp>CHARLES HENRY FALCONER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. The prisoner was given into custody to me—I found on him two duplicates, which led to where these articles were.</p>
